I have created a pristine CommandRobot from the Java-based Command Robot template. The only change I have made to it is to update to the latest version of WPILib (from 2025.2.1 to 2025.3.2).

When I deploy, I get this (over and over again) in the Driver Station console:

roborio Error occurred during initialization of VM Ôªø ÔªøÔªøÔªøÔªø
Unable to load jimage library: /usr/local/frc/JRE/lib/libjimage.so

If I do the same with the C++ version of the template, it deploys and runs with no problem.

Any ideas what is going on here?
